# Coding Standards

- Python 3.12+, typed with Pydantic v2 models
- Async for all provider calls
- Small functions, dependency injection for testability
- Docstrings on public classes and MCP tool handlers
- Use `ruff` for linting, `pytest` for tests
- No OpenRouter — call providers directly via adapter classes
